                            <comment id="14475651" author="paulk" created="Mon, 7 Apr 2014 19:00:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Added, thanks Andy! I will also add a convenience method &quot;localText&quot; or something similar to make getting the non-nested text a little easier.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14480448" author="paulk" created="Mon, 7 Apr 2014 20:05:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;As noted in the PR, this is a very minor breaking change in behavior but the behavior didn&apos;t match the javadoc (which described the intended behavior) previously anyway.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
